-- Polish lender Pekao Q2 net profit in line with expectations
-- 
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 01:32AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, August 5 (Reuters) - Bank Pekao <PEO.WA> booked a 6-percent fall in net profit in the second quarter, in line with forecasts, due to a one-off boost from the sale of a large chunk of its bond portfolio a year earlier, Poland's No.2 lender said on Tuesday.

